# Optional GitHub support issue integration
# These values are server-side only and belong in apps/api/.env.local or Vercel API env settings.
# Leave them commented out if you are not using the GitHub issue flow.
# Do not set optional values with format constraints to empty strings.
# Minimum fine-grained token permission for issue creation: repository Issues: write.
# Label assignment is best effort in v1. Issue creation still succeeds if the labels do not exist.
# GITHUB_TOKEN=github_pat_xxx
# GITHUB_OWNER=your-github-owner
# GITHUB_REPO=your-repository-name
